data.description: This all brick 4-bedroom, 3-full bath home in Marionville, MO is a must-see for anyone in search of a comfortable private living space. With its open concept layout, ample storage space, and numerous upgrades, this property is sure to impress. Situated on a sprawling 4.6-acre lot, this home boasts a park-like atmosphere complete with apple, cherry, peach, and black walnut trees. The detached 24x32 garage with electric provides plenty of room for storage, parking, and projects. Inside, the home has been thoughtfully designed with attention to detail evident in every room. New carpet, updated fixtures, and appliances, as well as new gutters, demonstrate a commitment to quality and attention to detail. The 6-inch thick walls provide energy efficiency and a comfortable living space. The kitchen is a chef's dream with tons of cabinet space, built-in pantry, granite sink, and separate laundry room. The master bedroom is spacious and boasts an ensuite bathroom with double closets, and the added bonus of a safe that stays with the home! The additional two bedrooms are spacious with large closets as well. The attached garage has been converted into another large master suite with attached bathroom! This large room has tons of possibilities! Keep it as a bedroom or use it as a large family room and additional living area! This home is perfect for families seeking a comfortable and spacious living space in a beautiful setting. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this beautiful property your own!
